      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is in concours-level condition, showcasing flawless factory paint and a pristine undercarriage. Mechanically, the high-revving powerplant benefits from recent preventative maintenance, including upgraded rod bearings and throttle valve actuators, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline is explored with total confidence. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the Variable M Differential Lock for optimal lateral dynamics. With zero modifications and a comprehensive service history, this is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically pure, collector-quality example of the last naturally aspirated M3.",
