      "description": "Available for acquisition is an investment-grade E46 M3, presenting in concours-level condition. At its heart is the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies to produce a linear, atmospheric 333 hp. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Crucially, the chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and the high-pressure VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed bushings and dampers that maintain the original N\u00fcrburgring-tuned damping profile. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the purist seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
